I move to amend amendment number 1 to HB3544
Of the printed Bill
Page 3 Section 2 Line 18
Of the Engrossed Bill
By inserting a new subparagraph f which shall read as follows:
"f. a general-purpose artificial intelligence system that is not
primarily designed or marketed to simulate interpersonal companionship,
including systems used for education, counseling, research, productivity,
or professional assistance."
